#Helm is a tool for Kubernetes that helps you install & manage applications
# We use helm for repetitive task and we can do app deployment easy, standardized and it can be reusable
#Helm is used to deploy from jenkins to Kubernetes
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

# Attach IAM ROle to Jenkins Server (EC2)
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
#Ensure EKS management console is created - attach IAM role to it; (Select the EC2 >> Actions >> Security >> MODIFY IAM)
   - Attach the policies to the IAM role - AdministratorAccessl, AmazonEC2FullAccess, AmazonVPCFullAccess, AWSCloudFormationFullAccess, IAMFullAccess 
